'''''Songs to Burn Your Bridges By''''' is the fourth album by  band . Originally released in November 2003 on the band's own label, Team Black, the album was re-released on  on  . In addition to rearranging some tracks, the re-release featured new artwork, three unreleased songs, and higher production quality.